The paper discusses the development of MLPerf Inference, a benchmarking system for machine learning hardware and software systems. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), augmented reality (cs.AR), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, given the focus on benchmarking and evaluation criteria, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.CV and cs.AR, and then cs.SY.
